18:28.402 --> 18:29.835
about his plagiarism.

18:29.903 --> 18:31.303
It was me.

18:32.911 --> 18:36.200
Someone else told Fermilab,
and he lost his job.

18:36.201 --> 18:37.634
Also me.

18:38.346 --> 18:39.243
And someone is

18:39.244 --> 18:43.212
sleeping with his ex-wife
and it's not me.

18:43.281 --> 18:45.481
I thought it was.

18:45.550 --> 18:48.017
Not anymore. Apparently,
just because I'm better

18:48.086 --> 18:51.153
than her husband doesn't mean
I'm as good as her contractor.

18:52.757 --> 18:55.024
Women, huh?

18:55.093 --> 18:56.492
I-I think you
need to go.

18:56.561 --> 18:58.561
No, wait.
Hear me out.

18:58.630 --> 19:00.229
Look, the three of us
could team up.

19:00.298 --> 19:01.364
There's one
small catch.

19:01.432 --> 19:03.132
Dr. Pemberton
has been saying

19:03.201 --> 19:04.934
a lot of bad stuff about me.

19:05.003 --> 19:07.470
But don't worry, I couldn't
possibly have done any of it,

19:07.505 --> 19:09.538
because I was with you guys
the whole time.

19:09.607 --> 19:10.873
I did it.

19:14.579 --> 19:16.278
Frankly,
I don't know what Linda

19:16.347 --> 19:17.813
ever saw in either of them.

